            The event is taking place at <strong><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/2PiVfrAdiV72" target="_blank">Paradise Banquet & Convention Centre</a></strong> at 7601 Jane Street in Vaughan.
        </p>
        <ul class="icons-ul icons-list"> 
            <li>
                <i class="icon-li icon-arrow-right"></i>
                The venue is at the corner of Highway 407 and Highway 400. Click on the map for a link to the venue, for transit and driving planning.
            </li>
            <li>
				<i class="icon-li icon-arrow-right"></i>
                Busses will be leaving from campus to the venue from 6:30 to 7:00 PM.
			</li>
            <li>
				<i class="icon-li icon-arrow-left"></i>
                Busses will be leaving from the venue at 11:30 to Downsview station and Finch station, and at 12:00, 12:30 and 1:30 back to campus.
			</li>
        </ul>
